outside of your body.

00:17:05.839 --> 00:17:09.470
Because I think a misconception
that people often have

00:17:09.470 --> 00:17:11.400
is that they're the
same size, right?

00:17:11.400 --> 00:17:15.060
So it was kind of this
paradox that wasn't essential

00:17:15.060 --> 00:17:17.579
