00:18:16.220 --> 00:18:18.380
And hopefully after
today your storyboards

00:18:18.380 --> 00:18:21.450
will be a lot better
than the one we used.

00:18:21.450 --> 00:18:25.212
But what I literally did was I
got the rough cut of the video.

00:18:25.212 --> 00:18:26.420
And I got all of the footage.

00:18:26.420 --> 00:18:29.470
And I specifically was looking
at this portion of the video

00:18:29.470 --> 00:18:31.620
